TY  - JOUR
AU  - Feldstein, Martin
AU  - Slemrod, Joel
AU  - Yitzhaki, Shlomo
T1  - The Effects of Taxation on the Selling of Corporate Stock and the Realization of Capital Gains*
PY  - 1980
Y1  - 1980/06/01
DO  - 10.2307/1885668
JO  - The Quarterly Journal of Economics
JA  - Q J Econ
VL  - 94
IS  - 4
SP  - 777
EP  - 791
SN  - 0033-5533
AB  - This study provides the first econometric analysis of the effect of taxation on the realization of capital gains. The analysis thus extends and complements the earlier study by Feldstein and Yitzhaki [1978] of the effect of taxation on the selling of corporate stock. The present analysis, using a large, new body of data obtained from individual tax returns, supports the earlier finding that corporate stock sales are quite sensitive to tax rates and then shows that the effect on the realization of capital gains is even stronger.
Y2  - 3/25/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.2307/1885668
ER  - 



